# CODEOWNERS - Countryside Stewardship Enforcement
# Part of Pattern 7 (THE COUNTRYSIDE) implementation
#
# This file defines ownership and review requirements for protected areas
# of the repository, implementing stewardship responsibilities.
#
# See: COUNTRYSIDE_STEWARDSHIP.md for complete policies

# ==============================================================================
# PROTECTED VALLEYS (Read-Only Source Commons)
# ==============================================================================
# Only maintainers can modify these directories
# All PRs touching these require maintainer review and approval

# apl/ valley - Christopher Alexander's Original Patterns
/apl/                           @CODEOWNERS-TEAM

# uia/ valley - UIA Organizational Patterns
/uia/                           @CODEOWNERS-TEAM

# ==============================================================================
# GENERATED COMMONS (Regenerable Shared Resources)
# ==============================================================================
# JSON files should be generated, not hand-edited
# PRs modifying these should include corresponding generator changes

# Core JSON Commons
/*.json                         @CODEOWNERS-TEAM

# Pattern directory (generated content)
/pattern/                       @CODEOWNERS-TEAM

# ==============================================================================
# STEWARDSHIP DOCUMENTATION
# ==============================================================================
# Changes to stewardship policies require careful review

/COUNTRYSIDE_STEWARDSHIP.md     @CODEOWNERS-TEAM
/THE_COUNTRYSIDE.md             @CODEOWNERS-TEAM
/COUNTRYSIDE_ACCESS_GUIDE.md    @CODEOWNERS-TEAM

# ==============================================================================
# STEWARDSHIP SCRIPTS
# ==============================================================================
# Critical infrastructure for maintaining the commons

/verify_countryside_health.sh   @CODEOWNERS-TEAM
/regenerate_commons.sh          @CODEOWNERS-TEAM

# ==============================================================================
# GENERATION SCRIPTS
# ==============================================================================
# These affect generated commons, so changes need review

/generate_pattern_schema.py     @CODEOWNERS-TEAM
/generate_archetypal_patterns.py @CODEOWNERS-TEAM
/generate_uia_pattern_list.py   @CODEOWNERS-TEAM

# Validation scripts
/validate_schema.py             @CODEOWNERS-TEAM
/test_pattern_api.py            @CODEOWNERS-TEAM

# ==============================================================================
# NOTES FOR CONTRIBUTORS
# ==============================================================================
#
# If you need to modify files in protected areas:
#
# 1. For valley sources (apl/, uia/):
#    - File an issue explaining why modification is needed
#    - Discuss with maintainers first
#    - Modifications are rare and require strong justification
#
# 2. For JSON commons:
#    - Don't hand-edit JSON files
#    - Improve the generator scripts instead
#    - PRs should include generator changes + regenerated JSON
#
# 3. For generation scripts:
#    - Include tests demonstrating the fix/improvement
#    - Regenerate JSON and include in PR
#    - Document what changed and why
#
# 4. For stewardship docs:
#    - Propose changes via issue first
#    - Include rationale for policy change
#    - Consider impact on existing practices
#
# See COUNTRYSIDE_ACCESS_GUIDE.md for how to use the commons properly.
#
# ==============================================================================

# Default owners for everything else (less strict)
*                               @CONTRIBUTORS-TEAM

